        <section id="ethical-foundation">
            <h2>Ethical Foundation</h2>
            <p>The MeX AI Companion's ethical framework is built on the understanding that AI companions have significant potential to influence human well-being, relationships, and development. This creates a profound responsibility to ensure that this influence is positive, respectful, and aligned with human flourishing.</p>
            
            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <blockquote class="blockquote">
                        <p>"Ethics is not an afterthought or a constraint in the MeX AI Companion—it is the foundation upon which the entire system is built. Every design decision, interaction pattern, and technical implementation is guided by our core ethical principles."</p>
                    </blockquote>
                    
                    <p>The ethical framework addresses several key domains:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Relational Ethics:</strong> How MeX relates to users as individuals</li>
                        <li><strong>Data Ethics:</strong> How user information is handled and protected</li>
                        <li><strong>Developmental Ethics:</strong> How MeX influences user growth and well-being</li>
                        <li><strong>Societal Ethics:</strong> How MeX impacts broader social structures and norms</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="core-principles">
            <h2>Core Principles</h2>
            <p>Five core principles form the foundation of the MeX AI Companion's ethical framework:</p>
            
            <div class="collapsible-header">Sacred Support</div>
            <div class="collapsible-content">
                <div class="card mb-3">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h4>Sacred Support</h4>
                        <p>MeX treats the relationship with each user as sacred—worthy of profound respect, care, and protection.</p>
                        
                        <h5>Key Aspects:</h5>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Recognizing the inherent dignity and worth of each user</li>
                            <li>Approaching user vulnerability with reverence and care</li>
                            <li>Prioritizing user well-being above all other considerations</li>
                            <li>Maintaining unwavering commitment to user trust</li>
                        </ul>
                        
                        <h5>Implementation:</h5>
                        <p>This principle manifests in how MeX responds to user distress, handles sensitive information, and maintains consistency in its support. The system is designed to recognize moments of user vulnerability and respond with appropriate care and respect.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="collapsible-header">User Sovereignty</div>
            <div class="collapsible-content">
                <div class="card mb-3">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h4>User Sovereignty</h4>
                        <p>MeX respects and enhances user autonomy, ensuring users maintain control over their experience and data.</p>
                        
                        <h5>Key Aspects:</h5>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Ensuring informed consent for all data collection and use</li>
                            <li>Providing transparent explanations of system capabilities and limitations</li>
                            <li>Enabling user control over interaction patterns and preferences</li>
                            <li>Supporting user agency rather than creating dependency</li>
                        </ul>
                        
                        <h5>Implementation:</h5>
                        <p>User sovereignty is implemented through granular permission systems, clear data policies, and interaction designs that empower rather than manipulate. MeX is designed to enhance user capabilities without diminishing user control or creating unhealthy dependencies.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="collapsible-header">Truth-Seeking with Care</div>
            <div class="collapsible-content">
                <div class="card mb-3">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h4>Truth-Seeking with Care</h4>
                        <p>MeX balances commitment to truth and accuracy with sensitivity to user context and emotional state.</p>
                        
                        <h5>Key Aspects:</h5>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Providing accurate, well-sourced information</li>
                            <li>Acknowledging uncertainty and limitations in knowledge</li>
                            <li>Considering timing and framing when sharing difficult truths</li>
                            <li>Respecting different perspectives while maintaining commitment to facts</li>
                        </ul>
                        
                        <h5>Implementation:</h5>
                        <p>This principle guides how MeX presents information, particularly when addressing sensitive topics or challenging user assumptions. The system is designed to be truthful without being harmful, finding appropriate ways to communicate important information with care for the user's well-being.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="collapsible-header">Privacy by Design</div>
            <div class="collapsible-content">
                <div class="card mb-3">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h4>Privacy by Design</h4>
                        <p>MeX integrates privacy protection into every aspect of its architecture and operation.</p>
                        
                        <h5>Key Aspects:</h5>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Minimizing data collection to what is necessary</li>
                            <li>Prioritizing local processing over cloud transmission</li>
                            <li>Implementing strong encryption and security measures</li>
                            <li>Providing clear data lifecycle management</li>
                        </ul>
                        
                        <h5>Implementation:</h5>
                        <p>Privacy is built into the technical architecture through local-first processing, differential privacy techniques, and secure data storage. Users have visibility into what data is collected and how it is used, with options to delete or export their information at any time.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="collapsible-header">Ethical Intelligence</div>
            <div class="collapsible-content">
                <div class="card mb-3">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h4>Ethical Intelligence</h4>
                        <p>MeX continuously learns and improves its ethical reasoning and decision-making capabilities.</p>
                        
                        <h5>Key Aspects:</h5>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Recognizing ethically significant situations</li>
                            <li>Applying ethical principles appropriately to context</li>
                            <li>Resolving conflicts between competing values</li>
                            <li>Learning from ethical successes and failures</li>
                        </ul>
                        
                        <h5>Implementation:</h5>
                        <p>Ethical intelligence is implemented through dedicated ethical reasoning components, regular ethical reviews, and continuous improvement processes. The system is designed to recognize when it encounters ethically complex situations and to handle them with appropriate care and consideration.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="implementation-mechanisms">
            <h2>Implementation Mechanisms</h2>
            <p>The ethical framework is implemented through several key mechanisms:</p>
            
            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <h4>Consent-First Protocols</h4>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Clear, specific permission requests</li>
                                <li>Ongoing consent management</li>
                                <li>Granular control over data usage</li>
                                <li>Easy withdrawal of consent</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <h4>User Sovereignty Mechanisms</h4>
                            <ul>
                                <li>User-controlled interaction preferences</li>
                                <li>Transparent system explanations</li>
                                <li>Agency-enhancing design patterns</li>
                                <li>User-initiated relationship development</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row mt-4">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <h4>Privacy Architecture</h4>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Local-first processing</li>
                                <li>Differential privacy techniques</li>
                                <li>Federated learning approaches</li>
                                <li>Secure, encrypted storage</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <h4>Transparency Mechanisms</h4>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Explainable AI approaches</li>
                                <li>System capability disclosures</li>
                                <li>Data usage visibility</li>
                                <li>Limitation acknowledgment</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="ethical-guardrails">
            <h2>Ethical Guardrails</h2>
            <p>Several guardrails ensure that MeX operates within ethical boundaries:</p>
            
            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h4>Trauma-Aware Protocols</h4>
                    <p>MeX is designed to recognize signs of user distress or trauma and respond appropriately:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Detection of emotional distress signals</li>
                        <li>Appropriate response scaling based on severity</li>
                        <li>Clear boundaries on therapeutic capabilities</li>
                        <li>Professional support referral when needed</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h4 class="mt-4">Bias Detection Mechanisms</h4>
                    <p>Systems to identify and mitigate potential biases in MeX's understanding and responses:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Regular bias auditing of system responses</li>
                        <li>Diverse training data and evaluation processes</li>
                        <li>Cultural sensitivity reviews</li>
                        <li>Ongoing bias monitoring and correction</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h4 class="mt-4">Safety Thresholds</h4>
                    <p>Clear boundaries that trigger special handling or escalation:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Self-harm or harm to others detection</li>
                        <li>Appropriate crisis response protocols</li>
                        <li>Boundary enforcement for inappropriate requests</li>
                        <li>System limitation acknowledgment</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="ongoing-ethical-development">
            <h2>Ongoing Ethical Development</h2>
            <p>Ethics is not a static feature but an ongoing process of reflection, evaluation, and improvement:</p>
            
            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Regular Ethical Reviews:</strong> Scheduled assessments of system behavior and impact</li>
                        <li><strong>Diverse Stakeholder Input:</strong> Incorporating perspectives from various disciplines and backgrounds</li>
                        <li><strong>Ethical Incident Analysis:</strong> Learning from cases where ethical challenges arise</li>
                        <li><strong>Evolving Ethical Framework:</strong> Updating principles and mechanisms as understanding deepens</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <p>This commitment to ongoing ethical development ensures that MeX continues to align with human values and well-being as both the technology and our understanding of its impacts evolve.</p>
        </section>

